ull,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"DearJoey","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEulNjy5o4vdjgC6HelC4abo7BkcNeqcy4n9DodScEqh59eBlvtBgia5zkLuxX2wTf0fA4ZSxI1gPp/0","content":"老板，我的报告格式有问题吗？（字体，段落分布等）报告呈现形式正确吗，需要换一种表现形式吗？（ppt,word或者其他）使用的数据有问题吗？报告内容上有什么问题是我疏忽了的？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7704,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492172404000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jenny","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoIfMsKLER8Nypic0GAEMQNhWH5ILCc3l1sO0iaB8nCIc9BLEdxIThXGnNtM55ozuBic03EicuCPictyib2/0","content":"需要要澄清报告的目的，使用者，使用场景，具体预期，格式要求，etc","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7644,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492072298000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Frank Wan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEJp53Pl3fVDMmrsYbiboicLLjY2xagaHEvwsU5VZbF8OtVEn6icIUepE2Oh8Lpo3wOSx3E8k066fZkfg/0","content":"老板打回来的理由是什么？或许就是不行，改。那么说话的语气是什么样的，考虑对待自己的态度是否有什么异常，从而判断是不是对我有意见。有些领导就是想整走一个人，会故意刁难。<div>然后就问：报告哪些地方不行，问老板想要得效果是什么样的？</div><div>想要得效果必须用报告来实现吗？或许还有别的方法可以实现。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7634,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492056979000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Echo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay0b57ibH6T3V3jNd7HDHXPdJagbpJpZ0oYN9srsbXbOyiaZS0Cqia5uToJn7saia4Gpsd3G2eB7siaedh/0","content":"报告那来做什么用的？<div>你希望以什么形式呈现更方便你的使用？</div><div>有什么关键内容你建议我做进去，或者说别的报告效果你觉得比较值得我参考下？</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7574,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491967409000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; margin-top: 0px !important;\">虽然在动手做报告之前先多问一些问题，报告被打回来重新做的可能性会降低很多，但是也有可能因为一些原因，未能获知老板的真实需求，这个时候可能就需要再跟老板沟通一次，如果我是小明的话，我可能会问以下一些问题：</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">1、这份报告的整体思路是不是出现了偏差？（如果回答是的话，再问思路需要从哪些角度去进行调整）</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">2、<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">这份报告的重点是否不够明确？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">3、<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">这份报告是否欠缺一些数据？主要是哪类数据呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">4、<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">这份报告的用词是否有不妥当之处？主要在哪些地方呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">5、<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">是否需要再多加一些图片到报告里？重点是哪些方面的图片呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">还有很多问题是可以问的，主要根据当时的实际情况，有时候可能也要看一下老板的神情，可能会得到一些真实的反馈。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7543,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491919376000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"文","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEuUJBibwaegwqwa7rXILx7WPapDW7tTnawmINtpCLZRonooMm0ezL1xuuMLrs1trOmgp0gmOpYOuk/0","content":"<p>是自己的原因？老板想要的报告是怎么样的，老板想要了解哪些信息。我可以用怎样的方式来呈现这些信息。是老板的原因？老板最近是不是心情不太好，还是因为别的事情这样，或者老板的风格就是这样的？</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7496,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491876101000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-09","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FZibDrTsS1osmryDqKeuAvlF9licJ4nKDicnJ1HjwXTbvxdlVJj5oBJgqhR72iaGMxLcib1jJGsyWnUnj/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">澄清隐藏偏差</span></p><p>工作重做</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">澄清什么呢？</span><br></p><p>是我自己的原因？（比如质量太差、没有弄懂老板意思、）</p><p>还是老板的原因？（比如心情不好、替上级背锅、做事风格就是这样、因为别的事情借机发泄。。。我是有多阴暗把老板想的这么不齿）</p><p>或是环境的原因？（<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">比如</span>公司中上级对下级的态度都很恶劣、工作性质对质量要求很高）</p><p><b>如何澄清呢？</b>可以利用组织行为学里的归因理论。比如，观察细节（同级是怎么做的？已经类似的情况是怎么处理的？）、侧面了解（了解自己所处行业、企业、部门的发展动向）、直接提问。</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">补充分析&nbsp;</span>澄清了原因，接下来思考：老板的真实需求是什么？还可以通过什么方式解决？我能做什么？这样<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">问题可不可以解决？</span></p><p>总之，做事要就事论事，处事要知轻重识大局。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7429,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491731178000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"柚子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-08","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKQ9yoT3nbNKdxAfx36YXu2S1KS39tFaY2Biaj1Ax9EC2EFm7YL9S2bhnYO900iaLz2YBl7tPsiaN5msXdt9Z7ibzrD/0","content":"1.询问老板对报告的评价，了解对哪一部分不满意，表层要改善流程，利益出发点是是为了提高会议效率，真正需求是为了提高解决问题的效率。<div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7392,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491635643000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
